{"tid":2235710,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"csl/1010 5G竟然用左N3/N8 去解決左彩虹信號問題？","createTime":"2020-10-09T02:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T03:25:50.000Z","uid":111639,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"acbcd17b076cb871705ca5a414b366d558f5dddc","tid":2235710,"uid":111639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T02:06:17.000Z","msg":"測試手機：Samsung Note 20 Ultra 5G<br />\n<br />\n最近手痕續約上左5G為iPhone 12做好準備，咁新野都問屋企人借左部Note20玩一日啦，點知發現彩虹依個csl黑點竟然全程無斷，download app望，發現竟然用緊 900(N8) 同 1800(N3)兩條band做5G<br />\n<br />\n咁一開始我都以為係Samsung show 假 5G logo，但Speedtest下又真係上/下載到 5XMbps, 平時4G係完全load空氣<br />\n<br />\n香港5G唔係得 N1/N78/N79/N257 乍咩？點解會出現左N3/N8 既 5G (NR) signal 又用到既？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NcmJiWj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNcmJiWj.jpg&h=945533c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EtuVUuF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEtuVUuF.jpg&h=ccf0da29&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ey9rgH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fey9rgH4.jpg&h=189927c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4daba0fd2d54c0c00d6d0e87e01a538adf25c89","tid":2235710,"uid":255744,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T02:09:59.000Z","msg":"5G U/D 5xMbps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf33b615e3d7df29b67da9a0c779073229ca9063","tid":2235710,"uid":34874,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T02:12:10.000Z","msg":"本身啲頻譜都冇限用幾多G嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef66a4ceb718751da5d88d4de614796e3cbbb6dc","tid":2235710,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T02:12:43.000Z","msg":"走法律灰色地帶用GSM/WCDMA/LTE原有頻段改做5G"},{"pid":"d1a48a43f847f1c762b6696ffc39005c01121584","tid":2235710,"uid":111639,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid